name: Biden PC
overview:
Biden PC provides computer and networking services to small businesses in the Los Angeles and Inland Empire areas of Southern California.

Biden PC’s main focus is small businesses that have from 2 up to 50 employees that are looking for ways to increase employee productivity through the use of computers, software and servers. Biden PC can install Windows servers, windows XP PCs, Windows Vista PCs, an office network, a wireless network, as well as enable secure file and printer sharing on your internal network. They can also handle your website editing and desktop support.

Through their list of contacts, Biden PC can also leverage services such as web design, website SEO, print media creation, telephone and Internet service, and web hosting.
